_:N707ec178b2fa406eaed92a842c8bb931 <http://schema.org/name> "Satvir Kaur MP" .
_:N707ec178b2fa406eaed92a842c8bb931 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Satvir Kaur was appointed Parliamentary Secretary in the Cabinet Office on 7 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Southampton Test in July 2024.</p>\n\n<p>Satvir Kaur was on maternity leave from 7 September 2025 until 22 February 2026, with a phased return from January 2026.</p>\n" .
